{"tid":1869319,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"刻意拖慢 iPhone 系統案   Apple 被法國重罰 2,500 萬歐元","createTime":"2020-02-08T06:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T05:08:48.000Z","uid":159448,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"69b218c343e5e165ddd4b379848da1d26b0294c2","tid":1869319,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:24:05.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒日前報導指，法國政府日前就 Apple 在 2017 年，於未有通知用戶的情況下，更新 iOS 系統導致 iPhone 6、iPhone 7 和 iPhone SE 的系統降速，作出了嚴厲的懲罰。據悉 Apple 為了今次錯失，需要支付高達 2,500 萬歐元的罰款，相當於 2.12 億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApple 於 2017 年推出 iOS 系統更新後，不少 iPhone 用戶發現運行速度變慢，後來被網民踢爆 Apple 刻意拖慢電池老化 iPhone 的系統速度。由於這個舉動未有事先知會用戶，引發了很大迴響；由於 Apple 不容許用戶將 iPhone 退回舊版系統，逼使很多用戶需要自費更換電池，甚至購買新手機。<br />\n<br />\n法國調查人員於是在 2018 年，根據當地的競爭、消費和反欺詐法，對 Apple 立案展開調查。日前 Apple 跟巴黎檢察院達成協議，同意支付 2,500 萬歐元的罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/02/08/france-fined-apple-for-slowing-down-iphone/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F02%2F08%2Ffrance-fined-apple-for-slowing-down-iphone%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOq0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=540e4b64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/02/08/france-fined-apple-for-slowing-down-iphone/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"18a8a3c75b39b4be1e49b4d62359d786f4b6583f","tid":1869319,"uid":256215,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"用家體驗既野你識條鐵？"},{"pid":"e9776477ffb13b2bf0c8f35ad9a236bbba5e4bbc","tid":1869319,"uid":9193,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"罰咁小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5754d90ceb9a15a197de232f6302c3c2a6dc4d5a","tid":1869319,"uid":275238,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:27:42.000Z","msg":"罰兩億濕濕碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4980c62bc283840727489d8f58a4dc7848adce","tid":1869319,"uid":165